headline: Bally's, Rush Street Interactive, Crocs, Lovesac, and Norwegian Cruise Line Stocks Trade Down, What You Need To Know

headline: Is It Worth Investing in Norwegian Cruise Line (NCLH) Based on Wall Street's Bullish Views?
summary: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for Norwegian Cruise Line (NCLH) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?
